General.Name: Image Systems AB
General.Description: Image Systems AB provides non-contact measurement products and solutions worldwide. The company offers solutions for motion analysis of images from high speed cameras, as well as high resolution film scanning primarily used for surveillance in the defense, automotive, and research and development industries. Its solutions are based on image processing algorithms and contain measuring techniques for log sorting, saw line optimization, and board handling connected to automation systems in sawmill industry. The company offers TEMA, a software for analyzing high-speed film; TrackEye, a defense-related testing software. Image Systems AB was founded in 1983 and is based in Linköping, Sweden.
